				"id": "r1_72",
				"text": "<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Läkemedel</strong></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Substans</strong></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Administration</strong></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Dosering</strong></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Risk för NAB<a class=\"tableFootnoteLink\" href=\"#fnote_21\"><sup>a</sup></a></strong></div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"5\"><p><strong>Första linjens behandling</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1063921\" data-text=\"Avonex\"></a>Avonex</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1063924\" data-text=\"interferon beta\"></a>I<a class=\"index\" id=\"1063925\" data-text=\"betainterferon:se interferon beta &lt;$nopage&gt; \"></a>nterferon beta-</div><div class=\"tableLine\">1a</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Intramuskulärt</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">30 mikrog 1 gång/vecka</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Låg</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1063934\" data-text=\"Betaferon\"></a>Betaferon</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Interferon beta-</div><div class=\"tableLine\">1b</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Subkutant</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">250 mikrog varannan dag</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Måttlig</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1063945\" data-text=\"Copaxone\"></a>Copaxone</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1063948\" data-text=\"glatirameracetat\"></a>Glatirameracetat</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Subkutant</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">20 mg dagligen</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">?</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1063957\" data-text=\"Extavia\"></a>Extavia</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Interferon beta-</div><div class=\"tableLine\">1b</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Subkutant</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">250 mikrog varannan dag</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Måttlig</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Rebif</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Interferon beta-</div><div class=\"tableLine\">1a</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Subkutant</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">22/44 mikrog 3 gånger/vecka</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Måttlig</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"5\"><p><strong>Andra linjens behandling</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Gilenya</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Fingolimod</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Peroral</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">0,5 mg dagligen</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Ingen</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1063998\" data-text=\"Tysabri\"></a>Tysabri</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1064001\" data-text=\"natalizumab\"></a>Natalizumab</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Intravenöst</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">300 mg 1 gång/månad</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Låg</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"5\" class=\"footNotes\"><div class=\"tableFootnote\" id=\"fnote_21\">a. <div class=\"tableLine\">Neutraliserande antikroppar</div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>"
